    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a driver-focused BMW E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver instantaneous throttle response up to its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a precision 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal traction through apexes. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the weight-saving carbon fiber roof panel which lowers the center of gravity. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive inspection of the rod bearings and throttle actuators. While showing honest signs of use consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, the mechanical integrity and linear power delivery remain uncompromised.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
