      "description": "This vehicle is a stunning example of pride of ownership, balancing daily usability with enthusiast-grade performance. The exterior finish retains a brilliant luster, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014honest evidence of spirited weekend drives. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of quality; the premium leather seats are firm and supportive, showing only slight softening on the driver-side bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It has been meticulously maintained with a documented service history, including a recent comprehensive inspection and oil service. The tires offer plenty of life, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. If you are looking for a reliable, well-cared-for machine that looks as good as it performs, this is the one.",
